    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for Class II MRL 2 devices. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate adequate agreement with experimental NIH measurements across all five operating points (max RH ratio 1.61, within factor-of-2 criterion). The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device under the stated COU.",
